SKILLS defined specifically in Krynn
====================================
Last modified by:
Teth, Feb 19, 1997

U means skill is unnamed for players, N means named.

Number       Name                Info
------       ----                ----
Knights
--------
67530  N     rescue              Used by the Knights        (rescue ability)
67531  N     kattack              "                 (kattack special attack)
67532  N     block                "                          (block ability)

108111 U     prestige exp        Accumulated prestige of Knights of Solamnia
108112 U     prestige stat       Prestige Exp converted into a stat. "
108113 U     charity             Charity for the Knights' Armoury
108119 U     disgraced           Knight is not allowed to train, access the
                                 armoury room and lead team (contains age).
108120 U     armourer            Used to determine the 'Grand Master' 
                                 when 100.

Gnomes
--------
108200 N     build               Ability to build things (gnome race guild)
108201 U     inventions          Used to determine rank among gnomes (")

Thieves
--------
108300 U     sacrifice           Hiddukel may support you when stealing if you
                                 have sacrificed enough.
108301 U     stolen              A number indicating successfully stolen items.
                                 Stealing from potent victims gives more reward.
                                 Used to determine part of the guild level.
                                 (This is something like prestige for knights).
Wizards
--------
108400 U     wohs_level_mod      A skill modifier used to determine
                                 the level of a Wizard of High Sorcery.

Elven Archers
-------------
108500 N     evade               The ability toavoid getting drawn into melee combat.

Throtyl Hobgoblin Raiders
-------------------------
108550 N     wound               A bleed special attack.
108551 U     Loot donations      Loot donations that go towards ones title.

Templar Knights of Takhisis
-----------------------
108600 N      tattack            Combat damage special attack
108601 N      focus              Skill used for avoiding attacks
108602 N      sap               Combat damage/stun special opener attack

School of High Magic
--------------------

108700 N      arcane focus       Trainable skill determining how quickly a
                                 wizard can memorise spells  

108701 U      WoHS guild xp      This skill used to store the "guild points"
                                 for the WoHS.

Order of the Stars
------------------
108800 N     Spiritual lore      Trainable skill affecting spell effectiveness
108801 U     OotS guild xp       This skill used to store the guild points for OotS
